{"tid":1824250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九影相手足致電律師指被人用拳頭打下體！","createTime":"2020-01-14T09:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T16:45:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88f02b46b18f3ddf2519481e171d98c44f2c4e78","tid":1824250,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"[深水埗警署現場][後生是原罪]<br />\n<br />\n大約三時一名年青人在西九龍中心8樓拍照， 被警員無理拘捕。<br />\n李文浩議員及李炯議員在深水埗警署陪同被捕者爸爸， 期間該名年青人曾於警署內致電出來， 表示於警署內遭到警員用拳頭打（鼻）及（下體）。<br />\n<br />\n* 劉偉聰大律師到現場親自處理<br />\n<br />\n#黑警必須付出代價 #拍照已經是違法 #黑警無法無天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1520262148244383/posts/2511601405777114/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1520262148244383%2Fposts%2F2511601405777114%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeroHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=1968576f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1520262148244383/posts/2511601405777114/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"37d1a137737840d135012447a8b1cdeadb496d18","tid":1824250,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想救連登，試下依個方法</span><br />\n<br />\n【測試】熱門新功能&mdash;行動篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d214790de4cbbb1f7cc646ea91d2a6203846663c","tid":1824250,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"( please forward to your English reading friends, colleagues, etc) <br />\n<br />\nMan arrested after taking picture of Hong Kong police in restaurant, with councillor decrying incident as &lsquo;arbitrary arrest&rsquo; | South China Morning Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fho